{"tid":728844,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"30歲仔心跳90-110bpm正唔正常？","createTime":"2018-07-04T05:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T10:39:39.000Z","uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f3157722ddf646ef37aa768ee84a6114b08ffe41","tid":728844,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"用Apple Watch monitor左兩年，用血壓計又度過同Apple watchbpm差唔多。<br />\n<br />\n靜止狀態80左右<br />\n行唔100-110左右<br />\n急步120-130左右<br />\n跑步帶氧運動170-210左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n血壓上110-130<br />\n下壓70-80<br />\n<br />\n問過醫生佢話心跳同埋血壓都正常，<br />\n但係同身邊朋友比較好似都偏高，仲有人哋一齊跑步心跳都係140-160左右，大家有冇經驗，知唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890a779d455bad2fdaa8d79e0c800c00fe0b2fe8","tid":728844,"uid":30028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"同你差唔多 <br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1b3259fbbf833df8fcdc22cf170cc84594f577","tid":728844,"uid":37733,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"個錶壞左？<br />\n一般黎講<br />\n最大心跳率係 220-年齡<br />\n你30無理由去到210"},{"pid":"064b5552145c2467dd41fbbe35a3c831bf1750e6","tid":728844,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:27:26.000Z","msg":"減下肥啦死肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62f818478b3e99eccb721c4c267757e7de1f234","tid":728844,"uid":79524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"跑步170-210<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪跑到好辛苦<br />\n或者係apple watch量度錯<br />\n你驚嘅話 不如去做一個運動心電圖 24小時心電圖 或者詳細身體檢查包埋check做運動時嘅心跳"},{"pid":"e5ca208c87b885f6e174472cbc26c96e3d1db318","tid":728844,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1b3259fbbf833df8fcdc22cf170cc84594f577","tid":728844,"uid":37733,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"個錶壞左？<br />\n一般黎講<br />\n最大心跳率係 220-年齡<br />\n你30無理由去到210"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"我運動嘅時候會好高，170-210都見過<br />\n其實都跑好慢30-35分鐘跑4km左右<br />\n停咗跑緩步回落160 150 140左右⋯"},{"pid":"e7f6235d83be528e33411013e2153761b458c352","tid":728844,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"靜止心跳率<br />\n<br />\n正常: 60-80<br />\n易有心血管問題 &gt;80<br />\n運動員 60&lt; <br />\n<br />\n大部分人的靜止心跳每分鐘介乎六十至一百下，但職業運動員的心臟功能較佳，靜止心跳每分鐘只有四十下左右。負責研究的專家指，研究同時發現，每分鐘靜止心跳每增加十下，出現健康問題的風險便高百分之九，心臟病及中風病發率亦會升百分之八，建議市民可定期留意自己的心跳。<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20151128/00410_005.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151128%2F00410_005.html&d=MNrG5JtwMuDYEPeFXOW5Bp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f3d9b020\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20151128/00410_005.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最大心跳率 &amp; 運動心跳率<br />\n<br />\n最高心跳率的計算公式很簡單，只要將二百二十減去自己的年齡即可。雷雄德舉例，一名三十歲的男子，他的最高心跳率應該是每分鐘一百九十次。換言之，要有效消脂、增強心肺功能，他做運動時的心跳應介乎每分鐘一百一十四至一百六十一次左右，若心跳超過一百九十次就會有危險。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20041202/4480365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20041202%2F4480365&d=MNrG5JtwMuDYEPeFXOW5Bp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8635234f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20041202%2F4480365&h=bfcdcaf3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20041202/4480365</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論: 做運動啦肥仔"},{"pid":"1f00cb3737166da5728bf68e8ab065c66cc2320d","tid":728844,"uid":14