>http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20041202/4480365</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論: 做運動啦肥仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:35:48.000Z","msg":"咁依家keep住去做運動會唔會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n號個陣過190<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"跑*"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"唔該你搵個第二個醫生先, 再問下佢專業意見, 應該點處理<br />\n佢話你 跑步帶氧運動170-210 都正常, 可能呢個醫生都唔係好正常<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得突然太急去做劇烈運動都易出事"},{"pid":"2dc18e873d11dda07d544c055fce7ce2697665b3","tid":728844,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16697228bb2f5e76ebc3b82cec1331428096ef62","tid":728844,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1b3259fbbf833df8fcdc22cf170cc84594f577","tid":728844,"uid":37733,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"個錶壞左？<br />\n一般黎講<br />\n最大心跳率係 220-年齡<br />\n你30無理由去到210"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"220減年齡係建議你唔好過呢個數 唔係冇可能去到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"佢1分鐘跳210下, 即係1秒跳3.5下<br />\n諗下都知有問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893ec31efe846dcc51c1848bad59a793e16bd933","tid":728844,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:42:49.000Z","msg":"以前75<br />\n做返運動而家65<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d3b5da2bfd32778da994dbe1c295566cd30844","tid":728844,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dc18e873d11dda07d544c055fce7ce2697665b3","tid":728844,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16697228bb2f5e76ebc3b82cec1331428096ef62","tid":728844,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"